Feature: Login Functionality of Demo
	
	@ValidCredentials
	Scenario: Verification of Login using valid credentials
 
	Given User is on demo page "https://demo.opencart.com/"
	When User enters email as "aarthi.kumaresan75@gmail.com"
	And User enters password as "Aarthi@123"
	And Users clicks the login button
	Then User should be able to login successfully
 
	@InvalidCredentials
	Scenario: Verification of Login using valid credentials
 
	Given User is on demo page "https://demo.opencart.com/"
	When User enters username as "aa"
	And User enters password as "Aarthi@123"
	And Users clicks the login button
	Then User should not be able to login using invalid Credentials